entries.femaleVariant: Couldn't've been just a bit more careful?
He chipped you for free? Fuck off.
'Ey yo, man! You try to rip us off?
Oh, you wanna try? Go on, son!
I ain't dealin' with Pablo. I'm dealin' with you. That means you an' me got a problem.
But I was! And I gotta work out, y'know.
I'm short. Don't got the eddies to fix you up.
Stop whiffin' for a week, you'll have plenty. And if I don't work, we're both goin' hungry.
Fine... I'll borrow some. Go get yourself fixed up at the ripper's. Tell him he'll have the eddies tomorrow.
Yep. Gear looks a little basic, but it works.
So he didn't ask for any money? Nada, not even instalments?
Like I said, he just finished and said, "See ya next time."
That's the cut I got off Pablo. Don't like it, take it up with him.
Now, I could paint the sidewalk with your guts, but that wouldn't get me what I'm owed.
If anyone wanted to see a jelly-roll, they'd sit at home and look in the mirror.
